  <brief_title>Pain Evaluation After Anterior Cruciate Ligament (ACL) Ligamentoplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pain Evaluation After ACL Ligamentoplasty: &quot;All-inside&quot; Versus Classical Technique. A Prospective Randomised Comparative Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
